{"title": "Golden Milestone", "description": "Frank Boreham was a well known preacher who served in England, Australia, and New Zealand. He published dozens of books and thousands of editorials during his lifetime, with no sign of slowing down, even up until his death at age 88. He wrote with a distinctive style, seeming to be able to draw a spiritual lesson out of any conceivable topic.<br><br>In this volume, the author has \"tried to point out a few of the things that make [the world] so loveable. If something I have said,\" he writes, \"makes somebody somewhere more glad to be alive, I shall be inclined to forgive this truant pen of mine its inordinate garrulity.\" - Summary by Devorah Allen", "duration": 24455, "language": "English", "authors": [{"id": "7199", "name": "Frank W. Boreham"}], "coverArt": "https://archive.org/download/goldenmilestone_2103_librivox/golden_milestone_2103.jpg", "copyright_year": "1919", "genres": ["Christianity - Other"], "supporters": [{"role": "Read by", "name": "LibriVox Volunteers"}, {"role": "Book Coordinator", "name": "Devorah Allen"}, {"role": "Meta Coordinator", "name": "Devorah Allen"}, {"role": "Proof Listener", "name": "KHand"}], "sections": [{"section": 0, "title": "By Way of Introduction", "readers": [11084], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/goldenmilestone_2103_librivox/goldenmilestone_00_boreham_64kb.mp3", "duration": 104}, {"section": 1, "title": "Pt 1, Ch 1: Sleepy Hollow", "readers": [14499], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/goldenmilestone_2103_librivox/goldenmilestone_01_boreham_64kb.mp3", "duration": 931}, {"section": 2, "title": "Pt 1, Ch 2: A Faggot of Thunderbolts", "readers": [10995], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/goldenmilestone_2103_librivox/goldenmilestone_02_boreham_64kb.mp3", "duration": 1058}, {"section": 3, "title": "Pt 1, Ch 3: The First Swallow", "readers": [15707], "path": "https://www.archive.org/download/goldenmilestone_2103_librivox/goldenmilestone_03_boreham_64kb.mp3"